ABUJA – PRESIDENT of the Senate, Senator Ahmad Lawan on Tuesday welcomed the Chief Whip, Senator Orji Uzor Kalu, All Progressives Congress, APC, Abia North back to the Hallowed Chamber. Senator Orji who has been out of the Senate to particulate in legislative matters since December 2019, resumed today. Welcoming him, Lawan said, ” Welcome back our one and only Chief Whip. We are very grateful to God for bringing you back.” Vanguard News Nigeria Photo news: Lawan, Abaribe others visit Kalu after return from prison June 5, 2020 In "Photos" SENATE President, Senator Ahmad Lawan, on Tuesday read letters from the ruling All Progressives Congress, APC and the opposition party, the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, announcing names of Principal Officers for the 9th Senate. July 2, 2019 In "News" SENATE President, Senator Ahmad Lawan, on Tuesday read letters from the ruling All Progressives Congress, APC and the opposition party, the Peoples Democratic Party, PDP, announcing names of Principal Officers for the 9th Senate. July 2, 2019 In "News"